{"tid":661883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誘騙學妹裸身畫符化解車關　還發生2次關係","createTime":"2018-05-12T03:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T03:21:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09cd80c86c6232c1945fa29a5c6777066ee16b09","tid":661883,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"趁人之危最可恥！<br />\n<br />\n《聯合報》報導，台南一位女學生深信鬼神之說，林姓學長得知後心生歹念，騙學妹她近來會遇到跟車禍有關的劫難，必須用「特別的」方式化解，要求她脫去衣褲任他在身上畫符咒，並在違反其意願之下發生性關係，事隔20天後兩人再度發生關係。<br />\n<br />\n林男坦承第一次是用「化解車關」的方式誘騙學妹發生關係，但第2次只是問她「可不可以再一次」；學妹也表示第一次是為了化解車關，第2次發生的緣由自己也「記不起來」。<br />\n<br />\n台南地院依強制性交罪，判處林男有期徒刑3年6月，但第二次強制性交無罪，全案還可上訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180512/640_710957fa2fc72a5acef62a617a921252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180512%2F640_710957fa2fc72a5acef62a617a921252.jpg&h=19bfb456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180512/1352359/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180512%2F1352359%2F&d=U8lfYkp3pziho3dMdODr2p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=67667703\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180512%2F1352359%2F&h=db3720f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180512/1352359/</a>"},{"pid":"50fd386817f822b122dfd22246aa4d148b20a1f9","tid":661883,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"不是處，插完心安理得<br />\n其實男方有付出"},{"pid":"2cfdab8c84a0f6cbbc5addf13addde6fff9c1908","tid":661883,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"2次發生的緣由自己也「記不起來」<br />\n<br />\n所以説"},{"pid":"68a3e92d9920266e4ebff8a1d8f7b11bd3d39a89","tid":661883,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cfdab8c84a0